args: You can't let yourself be tired yet;\nour work has only begun!

I can't believe you have so much energy.
We've been fighting for days without end,
yet you're spending all of your downtime
tending to the sick and wounded.
I just want to help people.

Oh, I'd say you're doing that. In fact,
I'd say you're working above and beyond
what your average nurse would do by
making your own medicine and such.
Well, many small towns and villages don't\nhave doctors or healing-magic users.
And those are the people I want to help,\neven if it isn't technically within my\njob description.
Now then, are you ready to get moving?\nI have to deliver this medicine, stat!
Thank you, Aeleen! This should have\nmy wife back to her old self again!
I'm glad to hear it. Please tell her that\nI would love to see her again.
Thank you for helping me before, Aeleen.\nOh, but lately I've had this strange cough...
Here, let me give you something for it.
Wow, everyone really seems to love you.\nYou have so many patients now!
＂Love＂ is probably a little much.\nI'm just trying to help.
Yeah! Why would anyone love someone\nlike her?
Don't talk to the nurse like that!
I'm so sorry for his behavior, Aeleen.\nHe loves you—he's simply too shy\nto admit it.
Oh dear, someone seems to hate me.\nDid you take the medicine I gave you?
I'm sorry. I've tried everything,\nbut he simply refuses to take it.
You shouldn't cause such trouble\nfor your poor mother, child.
If you refuse to take your medicine,\nyou're only going to get sick again.
I won't take anything YOU give me!
Hmm... This is a tough one.
Well, well, well! If it ain't the lady\nwhat's passin' out free goodies.
Yer the one givin' folks medicine, yeah?
Right?! We deserve it much as anyone!\nPlus, uh... Oooo! My stomach!
Sounds like SOMEONE needs medicine!\nNow hand it over, lady!
Let me take care of this, Aeleen.
I have this under control, thank you.\nNow let me see what I have to deal\nwith that stomach issue of yours...
Yeah, these guys are nothing but crooks!\nThey've been stealing our medicine and\nselling it on the black market for ages!
Shoulda kept yer mouths shut...\nNow YER gonna need medicine!
You are terrible! The people here are doing\ntheir best to fight their illnesses, and you\nwould seek to PROFIT from that?!
Shut up and make with the goods, lady!
Unless you wanna be dippin' into your\nown supply once we work ya over!
Are you crazy?! Put that knife away!\nThere are children everywhere!
Go on and grab the goodies!\nI'll carve this one up reeeal nice...
Bwaaa ha ha! Sure thing, boss!
Looks like we got us a brave little brat.\nGet lost, kid!
The hell is up with this dame?\nLet go'a me already!
Nurses don't just save lives...\nSome of us also take them.
What are you waitin' for?!\nGet this dame already!
Let's see how much you talk when I\nCRACK YOUR FACE OPEN LIKE A\nFREAKIN' WALNUT!
Yeah, you did. But you ALSO drove those\nthugs off without anyone getting hurt.
But now everyone is terrified of me.
I'm sorry. I know that was scary.\nCan you stand on your own?
That's good. I'm going to give you\nsome more medicine—so make sure\nto drink it this time, all right?
Now please don't hurt me! Pleeeeease!
Wait! You don't have to run from... *sigh*
Well, at least you got him to\ntake his medicine, right?
This is hardly how I dreamed my career\nas a nurse would play out.
Did I actually say I'd crack someone's\nhead open like a WALNUT?
Everyone, wait! Let's start over!\nI can be kiiiind!
